::DarkMouse::

She stood up and jumped over the table. She ran up the stairs and 
went to the main bridge console.  She entered her codes and loked at 
BlackAracnia.
"You want me to self destruct the ship?"
She pussed a few buttons.
"It's set to your command BlackAracnia.  Give the computer the order 
and it will destroy the ship in two minutes. Just enugh time for us 
to fight our way out of here and trap the Maximals inside."
